      "rationale": "Validation activities used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry with bovine blood analogue fluid at adult CPB flow conditions. These activities are representative of the original adult COU. The expanded paediatric low-flow regime (0.8–3 L/min) was not included in any validation activity; however, this gap was not flagged as a limiting condition in the assessment record, and no re-validation evidence has been linked.",
