    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at this model risk level. The assessment team concluded that the CFD model is sufficiently credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the documented COU. The team noted that the clinical use case has grown to include paediatric patients at lower flow rates since the 2020 validation campaign, but judged that the existing validation evidence provides adequate coverage pending a planned future re-validation study. No supplemental validation data covering the expanded 0.8–3 L/min paediatric envelope were reviewed or linked in this assessment record.",
